<text top="73" left="90" width="89" height="14" font="1">Fifty-first year</text>
<text top="73" left="717" width="111" height="14" font="1">6 November 1996</text>
<text top="109" left="122" width="327" height="14" font="7"><b>The President: </b>I take it that all the members of the</text>
<text top="127" left="90" width="358" height="14" font="1">Council have now marked their ballots. I ask the</text>
<text top="145" left="90" width="290" height="14" font="1">Conference Officer to collect the ballot papers.</text>
