<text top="235" left="90" width="58" height="14" font="1">collected.</text>
<text top="271" left="121" width="327" height="14" font="1">The tellers will now count the ballots. There will be</text>
<text top="289" left="90" width="358" height="14" font="1">two independent countings of the ballots, one by each teller.</text>
<text top="325" left="243" width="8" height="14" font="1">*</text>
<text top="325" left="265" width="8" height="14" font="1">*</text>
<text top="325" left="288" width="8" height="14" font="1">*</text>
<text top="361" left="121" width="327" height="14" font="7"><b>The President: </b>The result of the voting is as follows:</text>
<text top="397" left="90" width="154" height="14" font="1">Number of ballot papers:</text>
<text top="397" left="433" width="15" height="14" font="1">15</text>
<text top="415" left="90" width="163" height="14" font="1">Number of invalid ballots:</text>
